Extraordinary personal stories from around the world: today, Al Qaeda's first suicide attack in Afghanistan remembered by survivor Mohammed Fahim Dashty. Also Suciwati, the campaigning widow of Indonesia's leading human rights activist. And singer Jemma Pixie Hixon, who has become an international star without leaving home. Show less